","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8r9","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/rinse-nose-mouth-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Rinsing the nose and mouth in ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ghatafan reported: I entered the home of Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and I found him performing ablution. Then, I saw him rinsing his nose and mouth, and he said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would do so two or three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38968,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/02\/ali-testifies-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Ali testifies for Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and the best after him is Umar. Then, Allah will place goodness wherever He wishes.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 922 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/19\/sunnah-umar-or-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Are you commanded to follow Umar or the Prophet?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salim reported: A man from Syria asked Abdullah ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about continuing after Umrah to Hajj. Ibn Umar said, \u201cIt is lawful.\u201d The man said, \u201cBut your father prohibited it.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cIs the command to follow my father or the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39830,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/rahmah-for-granted\/","url_meta":{"origin":32435,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Lest they take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRejoice and give glad tidings that whoever honestly says there is no God but Allah will enter Paradise!\u201d They went out and announced glad tidings to the people, and they were met by Umar, may Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32435","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.